<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>진료 상세 - 홍길동</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/tailwind.min.css">
    <script src="/js/lucide.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 p-6">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto space-y-6">
        <button onclick="history.back()" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-800 font-medium mb-6 transition-colors">
            <i data-lucide="arrow-left" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
            목록으로 돌아가기
        </button>

        <form action="/doctor/treatment/1/complete" method="POST" class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <input type="hidden" name="treatmentId" value="1">
            
            <div class="lg:col-span-1 space-y-6">
                <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 p-6">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-indigo-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-600">
                            <i data-lucide="user" class="w-8 h-8"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">홍길동</h2>
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-500 mt-1">
                                <span class="text-sm">35세 / 남</span>
                                <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-slate-300"></span>
                                <span class="text-sm">내과</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <div class="p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-slate-100">
                            <div class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500 mb-1">예약 시간</div>
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-800 font-medium">
                                <i data-lucide="clock" class="w-4 h-4 text-indigo-600"></i>
                                2025-03-05 09:00
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-slate-100">
                            <div class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500 mb-1">환자 증상 메모</div>
                            <p class="text-slate-800 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                                두통, 어지러움
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-6">
                <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 p-6">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-800 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                        <i data-lucide="file-text" class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-600"></i>
                        진료 기록
                    </h3>
                    <textarea 
                        name="medicalRecord"
                        rows="6"
                        class="w-full p-4 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 outline-none resize-none text-sm leading-relaxed"
                        placeholder="진료 내용을 상세히 기록해주세요..."
                        required
                    ></textarea>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 p-6">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-800 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                        <i data-lucide="pill" class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-600"></i>
                        처방 내역
                    </h3>
                    <textarea 
                        name="prescription"
                        rows="4"
                        class="w-full p-4 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 outline-none resize-none text-sm leading-relaxed"
                        placeholder="처방할 약품 및 지시사항을 입력해주세요..."
                    ></textarea>
                </div>

                <div class="flex justify-end gap-3 pt-4">
                    <button type="button" onclick="history.back()" class="px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-medium text-slate-600 bg-white border border-slate-200 hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors">
                        취소
                    </button>
                    <button type="submit" class="px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-medium text-white bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 transition-colors shadow-sm flex items-center gap-2">
                        <i data-lucide="check-circle-2" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
                        진료 완료 처리
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>

    <script>
        lucide.createIcons();
    </script>
</body>
</html>
